                    <p style="color:#ffffff;background-color:#ffffff;"><span style="color:#313140;font-size:15pt;">Payment Policy&nbsp;</span><span style="color:#515164;font-size:10.5pt;">(Updated on August, 2023)</span></p>
                    <p><br></p>
